If your mpif90 is properly built and set up with the same Fortran compiler you are using, it appears that either you didn&#39;t build the netcdf Fortran 90 modules with that compiler, or you didn&#39;t set the include path for the netcdf modules.  This would work the same with mpif90 as with the underlying Fortran compiler.<span class="HOEnZb"><font color="#888888"><br>

